  "detailed_description": "<h1>Deluxe Edition</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129050/extras/1d8c13513ea314f123cd9ef1de140496.avif?t=1680283059\" width=630 height=141 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129050/extras/0cae3df141c8874950ac2f091c039fd0.avif?t=1680283059\" width=640 height=360 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A super special deluxe edition which contains:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> The game<br></li><li> A 60-page book telling the story of the game<br></li><li> 3 exclusive wallpapers<br></li><li> The game soundtrack (5 original songs)<br></li><li> The game sketchbook<br></li><li> 5 Steampunk coloring pages</li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129050/extras/c722f601885d4482df26f55efb45336a.avif?t=1680283059\" width=630 height=141 /></span><br><strong><i>REX </i></strong>it's a <strong><i>Roguelike/Shoot'em'up/Melee</i></strong> game with infinite gameplay and a variety of features and builds. You will control Rex, an alcoholic cat with a weak memory but a noble mission: to save the world from the evil Draconians.<br><br>You will fight against them in different scenarios with various builds, powers, and magic. Each round, the enemies become stronger and appear in greater numbers, but you will also become stronger.<br><br>You and Rex are the world's last hope, so create a powerful build, climb the leaderboard, and save the world in this beautiful steampunk magic fantasy.<br>                                                            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129050/extras/7e48a853788c3dce9cdea3d65c07a624.poster.avif?t=1680283059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129050/extras/7e48a853788c3dce9cdea3d65c07a624.webm?t=1680283059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129050/extras/7e48a853788c3dce9cdea3d65c07a624.mp4?t=1680283059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129050/extras/76eb295217d6d9cb09c9f9fc48a3ff50.avif?t=1680283059\" width=630 height=141 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 3 different scenarios<br></li><li> Melee mechanics<br></li><li>  Roguelike Deckbuilder mechanics<br></li><li> Steampunk Theme<br></li><li> 1 boss every 20 levels<br></li><li>A leaderboard system, with world, national and local ranks.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129050/extras/810e8959f858ccaa37008413ee71d19d.avif?t=1680283059\" width=630 height=141 /></span>",
